0:
”Alexa, open Water Reporter Assistant”
”What watershed am I in?”
”What are the swimming conditions near me”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: water reporter assistant
Developer Terms of Use
des: Water Reporter supports over 100 watershed organizations across the US collect, manage, and share the health of their local stream, river, or lake. Using data collected by our thousands of users, we can help answer helpful questions such as the watershed you are standing in as well as get the latest swimming conditions based on our partners at Swim Guide. This Alexa Action supports users in gaining a better understanding of the health of their waterway specific to surface water quality conditions, and learn more about the groups working to keep a pulse on their local waterbody.
